name: Vote Shop
greeting: Hello and welcome to the exclusive vote shop. This shop is our way of saying "Thank You" for voting for our server. Enjoy :)

_details.desc: ^ffcb4aThe most powerful medium of Chi in Perfect World.Can be used to refine your equipment at any Elderor trade for Dice Tickets in the Cube of Fate.
^ffcb4aSpeak to the whole world.^00ffffPut it in your Inventory to speak in the World Channel. Must be at least level 5.
^ffcb4aMysterious stone.^00ffffTeleports you to previously activated waypoint.Right click to use. ^00ffffCannot be used in combat.^ff8400Event Boutique Only
^ffcb4aBadge of a Wraith officer.^00ffffTake this to the Commander-in-chief to gain 25 Reputation.

^ffcb4aA Chi Stone of Perfect World that has evolved over countless millennia.Yiyuan Stones are the smallest unit of condensed Chi.Used for making Weapon Charms, repairing Shattered Gear, andreplenishing your Aerogear's Acceleration or your Genie's Stamina.
^ffcb4aLike a normal inventory stone... only SUPER!Use it at the Inventory Master to extend yourinventory to the maximum capacity of 64.
^ffcb4aLike a normal safe stone... only SUPER!Use it at the Inventory Master to extend yoursafe to the maximum capacity of 80.

^ffcb4aOne of the most useful items that everyone should try to get their hands on.^00ffffThis item prevents EXP Loss, Item Drop, and Gear Shatter upon death when in inventory.Has no effect in Territory Wars, Arenas, and some other locations.
^ffcb4aUsed to increase the efficiency of your training.^00ffffEarn 50% more EXP and Spirit while killing mobs.^00ffffLasts for one hour.
^ffcb4aAn amazing card of the cube. Can be used to trade for Robber Card and Bully Card in Cube of Fate.^00ffffCan be taken out of Cube of Fate.
^00ffff20 pages can be make into a skill book.
^ffcb4aCan be combined into an advanced skill book if you have 30 of it.
^ffcb4aA Mystical Page with ancient scriptures.Vital in creating Demon/Sage Skill Books for each class.Use at the Mystical Librarian in City of a Thousand Streams.
^ffcb4aUse 20 Apocalypse Pages at the Fire Forge in Old Heaven's Tear to acquire a skill book.Medium Ink is also needed.
^ffcb4aUse 20 Chrono Pages at the Fire Forge in Old Heaven's Tear to acquire a skill book.Medium Ink is also needed.
